{"tid":1227071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太古廣場巴打好好安息","createTime":"2019-06-15T14:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T14:37:05.000Z","uid":6457,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"040c2453d571fe92e2e2544ae68d578fc2d81f22","tid":1227071,"uid":6457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:28:02.000Z","msg":"r.i.p<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/keFs0qD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkeFs0qD.png&h=6278de14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd5b9af2c54379bb08fd4f5f94ebec506ef096bf","tid":1227071,"uid":46729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3bea719845466cda0249d9e62fed449bf1a362a","tid":1227071,"uid":6457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dcf683c0b2cf2c915981a1321e13996772e8b05","tid":1227071,"uid":123050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:29:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>行政機關濫用權力之審判</strong></span><br />\n二戰末期，納粹德國敗局已現，佛斯曼醫師、門格勒、拉舍爾三人的命運也隨著戰爭快速流轉。1945年時，拉舍爾因犯罪而被處死，和被他殺死的許多人一樣，葬身於達豪集中營裡。而門格勒假扮成一般士兵，躲過追緝後流亡到南美洲，直到1979年在巴西意外溺斃後才被確認身分。而始終堅持人性的佛斯曼醫師則在戰火中存活了下來，1945年時游過易北河後向美軍投降，戰後以泌尿科醫師的身份默默地生活著。在惡魔的年代結束之際，三名醫師分別擁來了他們各自的結局&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpansci.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2F5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg&h=327c7f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左上圖：將人浸入冰水當中，藉此研究在低溫下人體的反應；左下圖：故意讓小孩感染結核菌，並切除腋下的淋巴腺，測試人體的免疫力；右圖：紐倫堡審判中，對卡爾&middot;勃蘭特（Karl Brandt）醫師的審判，他被控同意並參與非人道實驗和其他戰爭罪行，最後被判絞刑。<br />\n用屍體換來的規範－紐倫堡守則<br />\n堆積如山的屍體、骨瘦如柴的幸存者，那些泯滅人性的實驗震撼了全世界。1948年在紐倫堡進行的醫師審判，被告的醫師之中，不乏知名的科學家，如施靈（Klaus Karl Schilling）曾是國際瘧疾研究聯盟的成員，戰時卻刻意讓一千多名囚犯感染瘧疾來進行科學研究。科學家在戰爭期間荒唐的行徑，讓美國醫師里昂&middot;亞歷山大（Leo Alexander）動筆起草人體實驗中應有的道德規範，也就是今日我們熟知的「紐倫堡公約」，寫明了醫師在任何情況之下，都不得傷害受試者（除非受試者就是醫師本人）。而1964年在芬蘭舉辦的全球醫師大會更提出「赫爾辛基宣言（The Declaration of Helsinki）」，說明了受試者有絕對的權利了解實驗內容，保障了受試者「知情同意」的權益。數十年的努力之下，美國和其他國家都誓言杜絕非人道的臨床實驗，全世界都認為這種惡魔般的人體實驗不會再出現了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qp60jU2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqp60jU2.png&h=0f218e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/62254048_1233250940184671_5825174709460795392_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=af8a127ef43e169c16b9bc1668a17909&amp;oe=5D8A89DA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F62254048_1233250940184671_5825174709460795392_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Daf8a127ef43e169c16b9bc1668a17909%26oe%3D5D8A89DA&h=582c6bc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41260fb1a17d501c072d708163584eb3734d7927","tid":1227071,"uid":188297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:30:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2dcae3bfca3706d6d39baebf6c3072d676d7ce7","tid":1227071,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/2vqwyvX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2vqwyvX.png&h=bb4e424a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我々は個別の11人。ここで我々が倒れようとも、個別の自我が我々の意志を引き継ぐ。よって我々にとって死は意味を持たない。"},{"pid":"1fbb66f1a8e348b84aedf885cbfbd94f7a8029f7","tid":1227071,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:33:23.000Z","msg":"我地香港人會繼續為你爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579f36ff6b9693023357b91fb2d845311d742b85","tid":1227071,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:33:38.000Z","msg":"報仇雪恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19c2970543aae8da9edc745b15b4f68a4be2402","tid":1227071,"uid":41524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"請大家好好記住佢嘅名字"},{"pid":"52299bf9a492d4a19014890f992aa5606d38491a","tid":1227071,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yJrG4UN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyJrG4UN.gif&h=ad4f6bbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d4f62f69c4cdbed4855519e15d26016e31402bd","tid":1227071,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c19c2970543aae8da9edc745b15b4f68a4be2402","tid":1227071,"uid":41524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"請大家好好記住佢嘅名字"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:37:05.000Z","msg":"啱，有無人知佢咩名"}]}